imdb.plot outline: "You've Got. . . " brings you new conversations with the nation's top movie icons, musicians, politicians and celebrities every day. President Obama and Kelly Ripa have both been guests, not to mention Fergie, Matt Damon and everybody's favorite dancing talk show host, Ellen DeGeneres.
imdb.title: You've Got...
plot: Notable artists, politicians, thinkers and movie icons talk about the news and ideas shaping our world.::Joe Ruffalo

"You've Got. . . " brings you new conversations with the nation's top movie icons, musicians, politicians and celebrities every day. President Obama and Kelly Ripa have both been guests, not to mention Fergie, Matt Damon and everybody's favorite dancing talk show host, Ellen DeGeneres.::Joe Ruffalo
